featured_reviews.review_id:
Serene place of worship reminds the sacrifices of "Maula Ali alahissalam" and his family members.  It is a KHANKAHI MASJID situated in the vicinity of "Khankah e Quadria Sattariya", Mehfuz baug.  One of the finest and beautiful masjid AL in a taluka Chikhli District Navasari. The Foundation of masjid was laid by "Hazrat Mehfuzali alahirehma" the great sufi and vali of his time. It was rebuilt by his two sons sahibe sajjada Abrar Kadri and Muzaffar alaihirehma with a sacrifice of their cousin  Ashfaque alaihirehma who died of freak accident while working during the course of construction of Masjid.
Most of the people visiting this place are in search of solace and they really find their solace here,  i am one of them. My sincere tribute to all the above great people involved in the construction of beautiful masjid for their wisdom.
Jazakallah khair

Hazrat Khairu Shah Dargah Chikhli is a revered shrine located in the city of Chikhli in Maharashtra, India. It is dedicated to Hazrat Khairu Shah, a  saint who is believed to have miraculous powers.
The atmosphere is serene and peaceful, and the devotees offer their prayers with great devotion and reverence.
The offerings made by the devotees are distributed among the poor and needy, which is a noble gesture.
Overall, Hazrat Khairu Shah Dargah Chikhli is a place of spiritual significance and a must-visit for those seeking inner peace and tranquility. The experience is humbling, and the blessings of the saint are believed to bring prosperity and happiness to one's life.
